<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card box-shadow">

    <h2 class="card-title">About Me</h2>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 my-auto">
        <%= image_tag "thumb-1920-838010.jpg", width:'100%', alt: "profile image", class:'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            
            <div class="skill">
              <h6><%= skill.title %></h6>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-info"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenew="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width:<%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8 card-body">
        <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. At urna condimentum mattis pellentesque. Sed nisi lacus sed viverra tellus in hac habitasse platea. Nulla posuere sollicitudin aliquam ultrices sagittis orci a scelerisque. Malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Nibh nisl condimentum id venenatis. Augue lacus viverra vitae congue eu consequat. 
        Sapien nec sagittis aliquam malesuada bibendum arcu vitae elementum.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jooobs :(
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jooobs :(
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


